metadata.name: WTF is that?!
metadata.description:
WTF is that?!: Edition

On the evening of December 17, 2017, Space X launched its Falcon 9 rocket from Vandenberg AFB. It left SoCal residents bewildered, wondering if it was an alien or some kind of an unidentified flying object.

Elon Musk, being the troll that he is, then tweeted, “Nuclear alien UFO from North Korea.” So now you tell me, WTF is that?!
